article_title: Can Anyone Be Objective About Obamacare?

article_metadata.author: John C. Goodman

og.description: Take any book, any editorial, any TV commentary about Obamacare and what you will likely find is completely one-sided. Either there will be an exposition about all the benefits. Or there will be a litany of problems and harms. Is there any such thing as an objective look at health [...]
